Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8月20日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣上悠那动荡的暑假终于迎来了高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的黑眼圈好重啊  怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  菜菜子没和你一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说舅舅一会会带她来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微离开一会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得还能再见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件东西想要给您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要把它…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是非常珍贵的东西对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为您把它扔掉后好像非常寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.02,0:16:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当初收下它的时候非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭得几乎都看不清丈夫的脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原来是这么深爱着他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手里的东西是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不需要什么烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的同学们互相邀请对方一起来看烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却没有一个人来邀请我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家都是笨蛋所以在嫉妒我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以根本不需要什么烟火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让大家为难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件东西要给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}（便携式黑白棋）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你生日快乐  秀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你房间里的照片  我得知今天是你的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么要送我这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种游戏一个人是玩不起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请别人一起来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家全都是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起干傻事也是很快乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…  但是我把烟火…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后一起去道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊  又不是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是故意的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了  小勇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们能不能适可而止啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然跟着这样的母亲连小孩子也会学坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这也怪不得你  因为你根本就不会教育孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…怎么会呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊  你这臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小勇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不是我干的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流了好多血
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  救救她  救救她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  没想到他真的打过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请帮帮我  有人头部流血不止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  这是怎么回…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.74,0:18:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  先用长布条把伤口包扎好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:18:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长布条？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小虾  把这个借我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs22}（注：海老在日语中也有虾的意思）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对伤口进行冷敷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思  冰都卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗  鸣上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来送外卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小勇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来她已经没事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂爸爸  我要这个大的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师您是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能如此地为我拼命的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  是Loveling啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吗  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没错  小勇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  真的是太感谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或许忘记了一件很重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救生命原来是如此美好的一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这道理是如此的简单  但我却全忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你  我才想了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:21:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  你帮我找回的这份回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我一定会好好珍惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢  请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是天城吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？我们正好在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子姐姐让你接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  哎  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走起来真不方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.97,0:21:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是又把肚子吃坏了我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我们来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家换衣服花了点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚的好  晚的好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  麻烦大家照顾菜菜子了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅  你今天不是有工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我推给足立了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是难得的庙会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家给我买了棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那接下来和我一起去玩打靶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你们也玩个够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  一会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日庙会之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.87,0:22:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人并肩而行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不适之衣带渐宽  夏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.43,0:22:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间你这是在模仿什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这里还是成对地走比较正常吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我赞成熊熊的观点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那熊熊已经决定好对象了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你擅自决定个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.48,0:22:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊的对象是千枝  小雪和理濑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本就不算成对了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以熊熊来陪大家一起逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.75,0:22:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这算是输了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们输给他了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:23:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于鸣上悠的暑假的记录到此结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}魔女侦探Loveling雨伞\N紧急到货！！\N还附带我的放大镜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.97,0:23:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  狐狸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.57,0:23:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是我的Loveling雨伞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}（堂岛菜菜子）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.23,0:24:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐狸先生  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.27,0:24:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.26,0:24:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀地解决它
Comment: 0,0:00:01.72,0:00:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:18.06,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,100)}下条线索
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.57,0:24:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翘首以盼的修学旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.30,0:24:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小矮子侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.98,0:24:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不可以再对这个孩子出手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.38,0:24:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.64,0:24:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王的命令是？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.77,0:24:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对的！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.86,0:24:31.45,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}下集  翘首以盼的修学旅行


